data.description: The Parks of Dutchtown! Wonderful location/Beautiful new listing. One of the larger backyards available...and so much more. Only one owner, open floor plan, large windows allowing natural light to flow throughout the home. Both formal and casual dining. Lrg. primary bedroom downstairs. 4 bedrooms upstair and 2 full baths. One bedroom upstairs is oversized. Large landing/flex space looking over the den. All this plus much more. Come by today to check out this gorgeous home and FALL IN LOVE. Make it HOME!
